  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to describe the correlation between the cytohistology exam of
      patients undergoing thyroid surgery, and the predictive values of: suspicious clinical
      findings, preoperative thyroid imaging, and the incidence of thyroid cancer in cytologically
      negative nodes.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
